name: WEBFISHING
description:
WEBFISHING is an online (or offline) fishing game where you play as little animal people!

CUSTOMIZE YOUR CHARACTER! Collect fish to unlock new cosmetics!

COLLECT THEM ALL! Try to collect all 40 fish!

There should be an official server running for a max of 64 players! Otherwise you may start your own with the server exe! Started the jam 5 days late, but hopefully you like what I've made!

Controls are shown ingame.
